---
const repo = "https://github.com/GeneralD/Magia";
const traits = [
  { name: "Background", z: 0, delay: "0s" },
  { name: "Body", z: 26, delay: "0.4s" },
  { name: "Eyes", z: 52, delay: "0.8s" },
  { name: "Outfit", z: 78, delay: "1.2s" },
  { name: "Accessory", z: 104, delay: "1.6s" },
];
---

<section id="top" class="relative overflow-hidden pt-36 pb-20 sm:pt-44 lg:pb-28">
  <!-- backdrop -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 grid-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div
    class="aurora pointer-events-none absolute -top-24 left-1/4 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-brand"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="aurora pointer-events-none absolute -top-10 right-1/4 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-cyan"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto grid max-w-6xl items-center gap-14 px-5 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]">
    <!-- copy -->
    <div>
      <span
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-line bg-surface/60 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-muted"
      >
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-run"></span>
        Swift 製 CLI · OpenSea Metadata 準拠
      </span>

      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        NFT を、<br class="hidden sm:block" /><span class="text-gradient text-glow">召喚</span>する。
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-muted sm:text-lg">
        Magia は究極のカスタマイズ性と処理速度を誇る、プロのための NFT ジェネレーター。
        無数のレイヤーを合成し、抽選・組み合わせ・制約を緻密に制御して、
        コレクション全体を一気に生成します。
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <a
          href="#install"
          class="cursor-pointer rounded-xl bg-run px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-night transition hover:brightness-110 run-glow"
          >インストール手順</a
        >
        <a
          href={repo}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-line-strong bg-surface/50 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink transition-colors hover:border-cyan hover:text-cyan"
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path
              d="M12 .5C5.73.5.5 5.74.5 12.02c0 5.1 3.29 9.42 7.86 10.95.58.1.79-.25.79-.56v-2c-3.2.7-3.88-1.37-3.88-1.37-.53-1.35-1.3-1.71-1.3-1.71-1.06-.72.08-.71.08-.71 1.17.08 1.79 1.2 1.79 1.2 1.04 1.78 2.73 1.27 3.4.97.1-.76.41-1.27.74-1.56-2.55-.29-5.23-1.28-5.23-5.69 0-1.26.45-2.28 1.19-3.09-.12-.29-.52-1.46.11-3.05 0 0 .97-.31 3.18 1.18a11.1 11.1 0 0 1 5.8 0c2.2-1.49 3.17-1.18 3.17-1.18.63 1.59.23 2.76.11 3.05.74.81 1.19 1.83 1.19 3.09 0 4.42-2.69 5.39-5.25 5.68.42.36.79 1.08.79 2.18v3.23c0 .31.21.67.8.56A11.53 11.53 0 0 0 23.5 12.02C23.5 5.74 18.27.5 12 .5Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          GitHub で見る
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- terminal -->
      <div class="mt-9 max-w-md overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-line bg-deep/80 font-mono text-[13px] shadow-2xl">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-line px-4 py-2.5">
          <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f57]"></span>
          <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#febc2e]"></span>
          <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></span>
          <span class="ml-2 text-xs text-faint">zsh — magia</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1.5 px-4 py-4 leading-relaxed">
          <p><span class="text-run">$</span> <span class="text-muted">brew tap</span> generald/private</p>
          <p><span class="text-run">$</span> <span class="text-muted">brew install</span> magia</p>
          <p><span class="text-run">$</span> magia generate <span class="text-cyan">--quantity</span> 10000</p>
          <p class="text-brand-2">✦ summoning 10,000 NFTs… <span class="text-run">done</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- layer-stack illustration -->
    <div class="relative hidden h-[420px] lg:block" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="layerstack absolute inset-0">
        {
          traits.map((t) => (
            <div class="layer" style={`--z:${t.z}px; --delay:${t.delay};`}>
              <div class="flex h-full flex-col justify-between p-5">
                <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-faint">
                  {t.name}
                </span>
                <span class="h-10 w-10 self-end rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-brand via-brand-2 to-cyan opacity-80" />
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
